{"tid":2013954,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 電腦間唔中斷線","createTime":"2020-05-12T16:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T16:42:22.000Z","uid":19350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ba18a9b52036db3f33a9053c7b63ac6b6b9ad87b","tid":2013954,"uid":19350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:13:24.000Z","msg":"屋企用緊HKBN 1000MBPS<br />\n電腦就用aztech既homeplug連lan線再連router<br />\n成日睇睇下youtube/netflix會冇啦啦load唔到<br />\n(youtube用chrome睇 netflix用電腦app睇)<br />\n有時會變左冇網絡存取 有時就冇變 但都係load唔到<br />\n要去變更介面卡設定停用左個網絡佢再開先上得返網<br />\n應該就唔關個homeplug事 因為之前用tp-link既homeplug都有呢個問題<br />\n會唔會係關電壓或者牆身電線事 <br />\n但我打緊機既時候呢個情況唔會出現 淨係睇片先會咁樣<br />\n有冇巴打知點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好困擾 成日睇到緊張位就斷一斷咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cd0b9e1cf8bb63a518840fb7bab82b64c96793","tid":2013954,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:16:28.000Z","msg":"homeplug唔識"},{"pid":"2c8ae6b9409c00ca7f7945359d5c36d18151d3cc","tid":2013954,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"Router路由器 集中討論區(27)發問前請細閱置頂<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2003207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2003207</a><br />\nhomeplug本身就係bug<br />\n睇呢個post，玩mesh router啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5778d79d9adbd282a9c27bffc569d3aae58a775","tid":2013954,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c8ae6b9409c00ca7f7945359d5c36d18151d3cc","tid":2013954,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"Router路由器 集中討論區(27)發問前請細閱置頂<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://li